<bibRefCitation author="Griscom, L." box="[892,1122,786,808]" pageId="48" pageNumber="48" pagination="1 - 439" refId="ref117284" refString="Griscom, L. 1932. The distribution of bird-life in Guatemala: a contribution to a study of the origin of Central American bird-life. Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History 64: i-ix, 1 - 439, 11 figs., 2 maps." type="book chapter" year="1932">Griscom (1932: 396)</bibRefCitation>
